{"tid":2513941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：要求香港提高疫苗接種率 改革醫療體系對接大灣區","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T04:46:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ab810f3193202f6397062cac554e8490c0abb8b7","tid":2513941,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"衞健委：期望本港清零 推進疫苗接種鞏固抗疫成果<br />\n<br />\n國家衞健委主任馬曉偉，在醫管局研討大會以視頻方式致辭表示，中央高度關注香港的疫情，亦協助本港提升檢測能力，經過港府努力，本港確診數字回復低位，期待本港早日實現「清零」目標，恢復與內地正常人員往來。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，香港要做好疫情防控，包括加快新冠疫苗接種工作，不斷提高接種率、以鞏固得來不易的抗疫成果、深化醫療衛生體制改革、積極應對人口老齡化和深化大灣區醫療合作等。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389901&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGteaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=dac14486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389901</a>"},{"pid":"0970e5d67f7acfed673790ff18eb914c9a8d2b28","tid":2513941,"uid":177047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"港府可以抄考黃洋達<br />\n<br />\n篤數皇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a877e2b0c0d31325951e399a06772bdd04e4d028","tid":2513941,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"期望本港清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd7dfc0c0f0f2ebfd20604cd99a00c24870e3dc","tid":2513941,"uid":50327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"某程度上疫情都阻礙左統戰速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1325f0ee42952642a3666ddade1743deccd2796a","tid":2513941,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0970e5d67f7acfed673790ff18eb914c9a8d2b28","tid":2513941,"uid":177047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"港府可以抄考黃洋達<br />\n<br />\n篤數皇上<img src=\"/asset